<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="2020日本包装设计大赏，获奖作品也太精彩了吧！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-390387" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/uisdc-bz-20200927-15.jpg" width="479" height="480" /></span></p>
